  <entry>
    <title>手机使用tinyproxy给电脑开热点（共享代理网络）</title>
    <url>/2021/04/29/%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%BA%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8tinyproxy%E7%BB%99%E7%94%B5%E8%84%91%E5%BC%80%E7%83%AD%E7%82%B9%EF%BC%88%E5%85%B1%E4%BA%AB%E4%BB%A3%E7%90%86%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%EF%BC%89/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>SSTap全称SOCKSTap, 是一款利用虚拟网卡技术在网络层实现的代理工具。</p>
<p>SSTap能在网络层拦截所有连接并转发给HTTP，SOCKS4，5，SHADOWSOCKS代理.</p>
<p>而无需对被代理的应用程序做任何修改或设置。</p>
<p>它能同时转发TCP, UDP数据包。</p>
<span id="more"></span>

<h2 id="下载sstap"><a href="#下载sstap" class="headerlink" title="下载sstap"></a>下载sstap</h2><p>win下载链接<br>链接：<a href="https://pan.baidu.com/s/1pIEUD2sPAeFOFfRQeGJhjw">https://pan.baidu.com/s/1pIEUD2sPAeFOFfRQeGJhjw</a><br>提取码：6666 </p>
<h2 id="使用教程"><a href="#使用教程" class="headerlink" title="使用教程"></a>使用教程</h2><p>打开手机端tinyproxy，左上角菜单栏，点击热点分享<br><img src="/2021/04/29/%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%BA%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8tinyproxy%E7%BB%99%E7%94%B5%E8%84%91%E5%BC%80%E7%83%AD%E7%82%B9%EF%BC%88%E5%85%B1%E4%BA%AB%E4%BB%A3%E7%90%86%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%EF%BC%89/4.jpg"><br>点击分享热点无ROOT<br><img src="/2021/04/29/%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%BA%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8tinyproxy%E7%BB%99%E7%94%B5%E8%84%91%E5%BC%80%E7%83%AD%E7%82%B9%EF%BC%88%E5%85%B1%E4%BA%AB%E4%BB%A3%E7%90%86%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%EF%BC%89/5.jpg"></p>
<p>双击运行电脑端sstap软件<br>点击右侧加号添加HTTP/SOCKS4/SOCKS5代理<br><img src="/2021/04/29/%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%BA%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8tinyproxy%E7%BB%99%E7%94%B5%E8%84%91%E5%BC%80%E7%83%AD%E7%82%B9%EF%BC%88%E5%85%B1%E4%BA%AB%E4%BB%A3%E7%90%86%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%EF%BC%89/1.jpg"><img src="/2021/04/29/%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%BA%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8tinyproxy%E7%BB%99%E7%94%B5%E8%84%91%E5%BC%80%E7%83%AD%E7%82%B9%EF%BC%88%E5%85%B1%E4%BA%AB%E4%BB%A3%E7%90%86%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%EF%BC%89/2.jpg"><br>填写手机端显示的代理IP和端口，分组默认即可<br><img src="/2021/04/29/%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%BA%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8tinyproxy%E7%BB%99%E7%94%B5%E8%84%91%E5%BC%80%E7%83%AD%E7%82%B9%EF%BC%88%E5%85%B1%E4%BA%AB%E4%BB%A3%E7%90%86%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%EF%BC%89/3.jpg"></p>
<p>点击右侧闪电标识测试当前代理<br><img src="/2021/04/29/%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%BA%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8tinyproxy%E7%BB%99%E7%94%B5%E8%84%91%E5%BC%80%E7%83%AD%E7%82%B9%EF%BC%88%E5%85%B1%E4%BA%AB%E4%BB%A3%E7%90%86%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%EF%BC%89/6.jpg"></p>
<p>测试成功，点击链接</p>
]]></content>
